  "summary": "**本題單涵蓋**：\n- 圖的遍歷：DFS/BFS 基礎與應用\n- 拓撲排序與基環樹\n- 最短路：Dijkstra/Floyd 演算法\n- 最小生成樹：Kruskal/Prim 演算法\n- 進階主題：尤拉路徑、強連通分量、二分圖、網路流\n\n每個主題附有模板程式碼、典型例題與難度標註\n\n:::example Dijkstra 最短路模板（最小堆實作）\n**C++ Dijkstra 模板**：\n\n```cpp\n// Dijkstra 最短路模板（最小堆實作）\nvector<int> dijkstra(int start, int n, vector<vector<pair<int, int>>>& adj) {\n  vector<int> dist(n, INT_MAX);\n  dist[start] = 0;  // 起點距離為 0\n  priority_queue<pair<int, int>, vector<pair<int, int>>, greater<>> pq;\n  pq.push({0, start});  // {距離, 節點}\n  while (!pq.empty()) {\n    auto [d, u] = pq.top();\n    pq.pop();\n    if (d > dist[u]) {\n      continue;\n    }\n    for (auto& [v, w] : adj[u]) {\n      if (dist[u] + w < dist[v]) {\n        dist[v] = dist[u] + w;\n        pq.push({dist[v], v});\n      }\n    }\n  }\n  return dist;\n}\n```\n:::\n",
