          "title": "17.1 網路流",
          "summary": ":::example 最大流：Dinic 演算法模板\n由於有其他做法（比如狀壓 DP），難度分僅供參考。\n\n```cpp\n// 最大流：Dinic 演算法模板\nstruct Dinic {\n  struct Edge {\n    int to, rev;\n    int cap;\n  };\n  vector<vector<Edge>> graph;\n  vector<int> level, iter;\n  Dinic(int n) : graph(n), level(n), iter(n) {}\n  void addEdge(int from, int to, int cap) {\n    graph[from].push_back({to, (int)graph[to].size(), cap});\n    graph[to].push_back({from, (int)graph[from].size() - 1, 0});\n  }\n  bool bfs(int s, int t) {\n    fill(level.begin(), level.end(), -1);\n    queue<int> q;\n    level[s] = 0;\n    q.push(s);\n    while (!q.empty()) {\n      int v = q.front();\n      q.pop();\n      for (auto& e : graph[v]) {\n        if (e.cap > 0 && level[e.to] < 0) {\n          level[e.to] = level[v] + 1;\n          q.push(e.to);\n        }\n      }\n    }\n    return level[t] >= 0;\n  }\n  int dfs(int v, int t, int f) {\n    if (v == t) {\n      return f;\n    }\n    for (int& i = iter[v]; i < (int)graph[v].size(); i++) {\n      Edge& e = graph[v][i];\n      if (e.cap > 0 && level[v] < level[e.to]) {\n        int d = dfs(e.to, t, min(f, e.cap));\n        if (d > 0) {\n          e.cap -= d;\n          graph[e.to][e.rev].cap += d;\n          return d;\n        }\n      }\n    }\n    return 0;\n  }\n  int maxflow(int s, int t) {\n    int flow = 0;\n    while (bfs(s, t)) {\n      fill(iter.begin(), iter.end(), 0);\n      int d;\n      while ((d = dfs(s, t, INT_MAX)) > 0) {\n        flow += d;\n      }\n    }\n    return flow;\n  }\n};\n```\n:::\n\n**搭配練習**\n\n| ID | Problem | Rating |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| LCP 04 | [覆蓋](https://leetcode.cn/problems/broken-board-dominoes) |  |\n| LCP 38 | [守衛城堡](https://leetcode.cn/problems/7rLGCR) |  |\n| 1066 | [校園腳踏車分配 II](https://leetcode.cn/problems/campus-bikes-ii) | 1885 |\n| 1349 | [參加考試的最大學生數](https://leetcode.cn/problems/maximum-students-taking-exam) | 2386 |\n| 1595 | [連通兩組點的最小成本](https://leetcode.cn/problems/minimum-cost-to-connect-two-groups-of-points) | 2538 |\n| 1820 | [最多邀請的個數](https://leetcode.cn/problems/maximum-number-of-accepted-invitations) |  |\n| 1879 | [兩個陣列最小的異或值之和](https://leetcode.cn/problems/minimum-xor-sum-of-two-arrays) | 2145 |\n| 1947 | [最大相容性評分和](https://leetcode.cn/problems/maximum-compatibility-score-sum) | 1704 |\n| 2123 | [使矩陣中的 1 互不相鄰的最小運算元](https://leetcode.cn/problems/minimum-operations-to-remove-adjacent-ones-in-matrix) |  |\n| 2172 | [陣列的最大與和](https://leetcode.cn/problems/maximum-and-sum-of-array) | 2392 |\n| 2403 | [殺死所有怪物的最短時間](https://leetcode.cn/problems/minimum-time-to-kill-all-monsters) |  |\n| 2850 | [將石頭分散到網格圖的最少移動次數](https://leetcode.cn/problems/minimum-moves-to-spread-stones-over-grid) | 2001 |\n| 3257 | [放三個車的價值之和最大 II](https://leetcode.cn/problems/maximum-value-sum-by-placing-three-rooks-ii) | 2553 |\n| 3276 | [選擇矩陣中單元格的最大得分](https://leetcode.cn/problems/select-cells-in-grid-with-maximum-score) | 2403 |\n| 3376 | [破解鎖的最少時間 I](https://leetcode.cn/problems/minimum-time-to-break-locks-i) | 1793 |\n| 3385 | [破解鎖的最少時間 II](https://leetcode.cn/problems/minimum-time-to-break-locks-ii) |  |"
